OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Tens of thousands of Ukrainians are    
OL,6, pouring towards neighbouring countries 
OL,7, to flee the Russian invasion.          
OL,9,FIn the three days since the invasion   
OL,10,Fbegan, more than 115,000 have crossed  
OL,11,Finto Poland alone - some travelling for
OL,12,Fmore than two days, others joining     
OL,13,Fqueues 15km (10 miles) long at border  
OL,14,Fpoints.                                
OL,16,FThose fleeing are mostly women and     
OL,17,Fchildren, as all Ukrainian men aged 18 
OL,18,Fto 60 are being told to stay and fight 
OL,19,F- in some cases separated from their   
OL,20,Ffamilies. BBC correspondents met them  
OL,21,Fat the borders.                        
